Date: Sat, 14 Mar 2026 21:30:20 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] Replace FreeImage dependency with stb (#725)

Cherry-picked from main commit 15de7e6. Removes insecure FreeImage
dependency and replaces it with vendored stb headers.

Signed-off-by: cherry-pick from PR #725
